extendedData.value:
KEY FEATURES:
• 4 Innistrad: Midnight Hunt Commander Decks, with 2 of each deck—2 Coven Counters + 2 Undead Unleashed
• Each ready-to-play deck contains 100 Magic cards (2 traditional foil + 98 nonfoil)
• Both decks come with 1 foil-etched Display Commander, 10 tokens, 1 life tracker + 1 deck box
• Coven Counters and Undead Unleashed each introduce 15 MTG cards not found in the main set
• Reduced-plastic packaging

This bundle includes 4 Innistrad: Midnight Hunt Commander Decks, with 2 of each deck—2 Coven Counters and 2 Undead Unleashed. Each deck set contains 1 ready-to-play deck of 100 Magic cards (2 traditional foil, 98 nonfoil), 1 foil-etched Display Commander (a thick cardstock copy of the commander card with textured foil etched into the card’s border and art), 10 double-sided tokens, 1 deck box (can hold 100 sleeved cards), 1 life tracker, and 1 reference card—all using 98% less plastic than previous Commander decks, including packaging.
